electricityContract.terms: This offer is only available to customers with an applicable network tariff. Eligibility criteria apply, for terms and conditions see alintaenergy.com.au/termsandconditions or call 13 37 02.
electricityContract.variation: Alinta Energy's market tariff and feed in tariffs (where applicable) may be varied in accordance with applicable laws. If we change the applicable tariff, we will give you notice of any variations in accordance with applicable laws.

incentives.description: Eligible for new or moving customers, bonus credit applied on your first bill provided you are still on this Energy Plan at that time. Credits cannot be transferred/exchanged or paid out. Bonus credits limited to 1 per account in any 12-month period.

electricityContract.onExpiryDescription: 12 months from the acceptance date the contract ends. Unless you accept a new offer under a Market Retail Contract you will be put on our Standing Offer under the Standard Retail Contract (prices as published on our website).
electricityContract.additionalFeeInformation: We reserve the right to and will notify you if we change or impose additional fees or charges in relation to your energy supply. Fees and charges for work undertaken by your Distributor or Metering Provider are outlined at www.alintaenergy.com.au/feesandcharges
